# Environment Variables Template

# Contentful CMS Configuration
CONTENTFUL_SPACE_ID=your_space_id_here
CONTENTFUL_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_access_token_here
CONTENTFUL_PREVIEW_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_preview_token_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Create a Contentful account at https://www.contentful.com/
# 2. Create a new space
# 3. Go to Settings > API keys
# 4. Create a new API key or use an existing one
# 5. Copy the Space ID and Content Delivery API access token
# 6. Rename this file to .env.local and fill in your values
